<div class="SG_conn" id="module_1001">
            <div class="SG_connHead">
            <span class="title" comp_title="个人简介">个人简介</span>
                       <span class="edit">
                        </span>
            </div>
            <div class="SG_connBody">
            	<div class="diywidget" style="position:relative"><P><FONT STYLE="font-size: 12px;"><FONT STYLE=""><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">洪杰，<SPAN>国家注册高级黄金投资分析师，上海第一财经特邀嘉宾，</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">FIA</SPAN><SPAN>金融信息分析技术师资，中国黄金报社特约黄金投资分析师，财经媒体自由撰稿人。</SPAN>新浪财经、</SPAN></FONT><SPAN STYLE="background-color: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;">中国黄金网、</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">和讯、凤凰财经、汇通网、中金在线等国内知名媒体网站特邀嘉宾和投稿人；</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2011</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年被金融界网站评选为“优秀黄金分析师”;个人博客被中金在线评选为</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2011</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">、</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2012</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">、</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2013</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">、</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2014</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年度“最受欢迎财经博客百强”;</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2013</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年被中金在线评选为“年度最受欢迎黄金分析师”</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">,2014</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年被中金在线评选为“年度最佳黄金路演分析师”;2016年被汇通财经评为“最具影响力分析师”;</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2017</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年被中金在线评选为“值得信赖的黄金分析师”，同年荣获中国金融衍生品</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">100</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">人论坛“金骥奖”优秀专业人才“最佳黄金分析师”;</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">2018</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年在中国第四届金融分析大会中荣获“金融分析服务优秀奖”</SPAN><SPAN LANG="EN-US" STYLE="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;" XML:LANG="EN-US">;2019</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;">年被中国黄金报社（北京黄金经济发展研究中心）评为“特约黄金投资分析师”，同年被中国第五届金融分析大会评为“黄金分析服务优秀奖”</SPAN><SPAN STYLE="background-color: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;">。对于黄金、外汇以及股票都有较深的理解，有着丰富的实盘经验，善于把握一些中长线的投资机会，重视交易理念和执行力。</SPAN></FONT></P><P><FONT STYLE="FonT-siZe: 18px"><SPAN STYLE="FonT-siZe: medium"><SPAN><STRONG>QQ:2496517308</STRONG></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr> &nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr></FONT></P><P><STRONG><FONT COLOR="#ED1C24">在线咨询:</FONT><A STYLE="CoLor: rgb(156,90,60)" HREF="http://wpa.qq.com/msgrd?v=3&amp;uin=2496517308&amp;site=qq&amp;menu=yes" TARGET="_blank"><IMG TITLE="点击这里给我发消息" BORDER="0" ALT="点击这里给我发消息" SRC="http://wpa.qq.com/pa?p=2:2496517308:41%20&amp;r=0.4385545455407604" /></A></STRONG></P><P>&nbsp;<wbr></P><DIV><A HREF="http://vote.blog.cnfol.com/2011/" TARGET="_blank" DATA-KE-SRC="http://vote.blog.cnfol.com/2011/"><IMG BORDER="0" ALT="" SRC="http://images.cnfol.com/articles/461_1171668.jpg" DATA-KE-SRC="http://images.cnfol.com/articles/461_1171668.jpg" /></A></DIV><P><A HREF="http://vote.blog.cnfol.com/2012/index.shtml"