<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>周四（<span>8</span>月<span>29</span>日）现货黄金窄幅震荡后小幅走高，现报<span>1542.26</span>美元，涨幅<span>0.21%</span>，黄金<span>T+D</span>报<span>357.83</span>元<span>/</span>克。</span></p>
<p><b><span style=
'mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>·金银<span>T+D</span>连创新高</span></b></p>
<p style='text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>周三（<span>8</span>月<span>28</span>日）黄金<span>T+D</span>收盘上涨<span>0.57%</span>至<span>357</span>元<span>/</span>克，再创近七年新高至<span>359.01</span>元<span>/</span>千克；白银<span>T+D</span>收盘上涨<span>3.35%</span>至<span>4504</span>元<span>/</span>千克，创<span>2016</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>5</span>日以来的逾三年新高至<span>4521</span>元<span>/</span>千克，周三现货黄金探底回升至<span>1540</span>美元<span>/</span>盎司上方，现货白银刷新<span>2017</span>年</span></p>
