										<div class="content newfont_family">
							<p style='text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>周三（<span>8</span>月<span>21</span>日）亚市早盘，现货黄金略微走低，</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:'>现报<span>1505.26</span>美元</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>/</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:'>盎司</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:'>，跌幅<span>0.12%</span>。全球最大黄金<span>ETF--SPDR
GoldTrust</span>持仓较上日增加<span>1.76</span>吨，增幅为<span>0.21%</span>，当前持仓量为<span>845.17</span>吨。</span></p>
<p><b><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>·美股三连涨结束
金价重获支撑</span></b></p>
<p style='text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>本周因美股连续三日走高以及部分欧洲国家欲出台刺激措施，一定程度上缓解了市场对于经济放缓的忧虑，这使得黄金一度跌至一周低点。但是由于全球宽松的语预期，叠加经</span></p>
