							<p style='text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>周三（<span>8</span>月<span>14</span>日）亚洲早盘，黄金多空局势焦灼，金价收复<span>1500</span>美元<span>/</span>盎司关口。</span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:'>昨日晚<span>21</span>点<span>30</span>分左右，黄金价格则快速跳水，国际黄金价格跌破<span>1490</span>美元<span>/</span>盎司，日内跌幅超过<span>1%</span>。</span></p>
<p><b><span style=
'mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>·离岸人民币重回<span>6</span>时代</span></b></p>
<p style='text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>北京时间<span>8</span>月<span>13</span>日晚<span>21</span>点<span>30</span>分左右，离岸人民币兑美元汇率短线快速拉升，重回“<span>6</span>”时代，<span>30</span>分钟内从<span>7.10</span>附近拉升到<span>6.99</span>左右，拉升幅度超过<span>1000</span>点。<span>21</span>世纪经济报道记者采访的多位金融领域分析师认为，人民币汇率的</span></p>
