							<p style='text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>周一（<span>8</span>月<span>12</span>日）现货黄金小幅震荡，但总体仍处于<span>1490-1510</span>区间内，现报<span>1497.20</span>美元，涨幅<span>0.2%</span>。近几个交易日黄金总体交投于<span>1490-1510</span>区间内。此前，因国际贸易局势收紧及全球央行的宽松政策，黄金持续刷新逾<span>6</span>年高点，短时间存在小幅回调空间。</span></p>
<p><b><span style=
'mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>·上周<span>T+D</span>收涨
<span>ETF</span>持续刷高</span></b></p>
<p style='text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>上周五（<span>8</span>月<span>9</span>日）黄金<span>T+D</span>上涨<span>0.07%</span>至<span>343.4</span>元<span>/</span>克，现货黄金小幅上涨，多空继续在<span>1500</span>美元<span>/</span>盎司附近震荡，七月全球黄金<span>ETF</span>规模增长<span>26</span>亿美元，总持仓规模上升<span>52</span>吨至<span>2600</span>吨，达<span>2013</span></span></p>
