										<div class="content newfont_family">
							<p style='text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>周五（<span>8</span>月<span>9</span>日）现货黄金于<span>1500</span>美元上方震荡，受美债收益率和美股自低点影响出现一定的反弹，同时，黄金在突破<span>1500</span>美元关口后短暂处于超买状态，涨势暂缓。现货黄金现报<span>1504.01</span>美元<span>/</span>盎司，涨幅<span>0.2%</span>。</span></p>
<p><strong><span style=
'font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); letter-spacing: 0.75pt;'>
·各大区域市场黄金热潮涌现</span></strong></p>
<p style='text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0'>
<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'>世界黄金协会表示，全球黄金<span style=''>ETF</span>和类似产品上月净流入量为<span style=''>26</span>亿美元，持有量增加<span style=''>52</span>吨至<span style=''>2600</span>吨，这是自<span style=''>2013</span>年<span style=''>3</span>月以来的最高水平。数据显示，北美投资者正在主导<span style=''>ETF</span>市场，<span style=''>7</span>月北美</span></p>
